  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a pot with a knob of <strong>butter </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>tomato paste</strong> with <strong>half</strong> your <strong>dried oregano </strong>and<strong> half </strong>your<strong> ground smoked paprika </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>white long grain rice </strong>and<strong> chicken stock mix</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up until the rice is fully coated</p>",
