    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is fully coated, add 250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[375ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span><strong> cold water</strong> and bring to the boil</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Once done, remove from the heat and set aside (lid on) to steam until serving – this is your <strong>red rice</strong></p>",
