    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>remaining ground smoked paprika</strong> (save a pinch for garnish!), <strong>remaining dried oregano </strong>and your<strong> ground coriander</strong> in a large bowl with 4 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[6 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[8 tbsp]</span><strong> flour </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
