    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>chicken thighs</strong> to the bowl with 4 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[6 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[8 tsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and, using your hands, scrunch the flour onto the chicken until fully coated – this is your <strong>coated chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
