    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, drain your <strong>sweetcorn</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>drained sweetcorn </strong>with the juice of <strong>half </strong>your <strong>lime[s] </strong>(don't like it too sour? Just add a little!)<strong> </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Crumble in your <strong>feta </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>elote corn</strong></p><p>Chop the<strong> remaining lime </strong>into 1 wedge per person</p>",
