    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>chipotle paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)<strong> </strong>and<strong> honey </strong>with<strong> </strong>a knob of<strong> butter </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>in a small heatproof bowl</p><p>Put the bowl in the <strong>microwave </strong>and cook for 20-30 secs or until the butter is melted</p><p>Give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>chipotle honey butter</strong></p>",
