    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Mexican-style fried chicken </strong>with the <strong>red rice</strong>,<strong> elote corn </strong>and <strong>chipotle honey butter</strong></p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into a small bowl and turn out</p><p>Garnish the elote corn with the <strong>reserved ground smoked paprika</strong> and a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
